data.description: Nestled on a sprawling 10-acre estate, this magnificent luxurious home offers the epitome of refined country living. With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, this meticulously designed residence provides a perfect blend of space, comfort, and sophistication.As you enter the property, you'll be captivated by the beautifully landscaped grounds and the sense of tranquility that surrounds you. The grandeur of the home is matched by the practicality of living minutes from SPRINGFIELD.Inside the home, a sense of luxury greets you at every turn. Exquisite finishes, soaring ceilings, and an abundance of natural light create an inviting and elegant atmosphere. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring NEW appliances and granite counter tops.The master suite is a private oasis, with a spacious en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet, providing a serene retreat from the world. The additional bedrooms offer ample space for family, guests, or the versatility to create a home office or personal gym. A picturesque barn & greenhouse adds to the charm of the estate, offering countless opportunities for equestrian pursuits, hobby farming, or simply as an inviting space for gatherings and storage. The possibilities are only limited by your imagination. In addition to its aesthetic appeal, this home is equipped with a state-of-the-art security system that encompasses the entire property. With advanced surveillance cameras, motion detectors, and alarm systems, your family and your possessions are safeguarded around the clock. Whether you're at home or away, you can rest easy knowing your property is protected.All of this in the award-winning Willard School District!
